    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"stop trying to fit in... find peace in your own way\"... what does that even mean? like, is there actually a way to just... stop the noise without having to keep up this exhausting act anymore? because right now, it feels like the only way to actually be at peace is to just not exist at all.",
